name: Examining the Ex-Gay Community
description: Stories from the ex-gay and ex-ex-gay communities, two over-looked populations who struggle to reconcile sexuality with their faith. More information here. Full color, twenty-four page book that is hand bound with linen thread.

name: Hood Tracks — Lincoln Park Print
description: For Chicagoans who prefer hyper local... The second print in a series featuring local train stations as the focal point they so often are in Chicago neighborhoods. Printed on high quality matte paper, the prints fits perfectly in a standard 11x17 frame. If you'd like the print in a different size (or an additional 1-2 inches around the edges for matting) please contact me. I'm happy to make custom arrangements.

name: Letterpress Notecards
description: While printing a limited edition of broadsides and book covers for Called Wilson, I generated a small number of test prints that I've cut down into handprinted notecards. Each set includes five letterpress notecards and matching envelopes. Size is approximately "5.5x4.25. * Envelopes are available in red, white, and brown. If you have a preference, please let me know in the order!
